voc_to_yolo_converter.py
➤ Converts PascalVOC annotations to YOLO format.

person_model_train.ipynb
➤ Trains the YOLOv8 model to detect persons.

crop_person_images.ipynb (Optional)
➤ Crops detected persons from training images for PPE detection dataset.

ppe_model_train.ipynb
➤ Trains the YOLOv8 model to detect PPE items on person images.

person_model_to_onnx.py
➤ Converts the trained person detection model to ONNX format.

ppe_model_to_onnx.py
➤ Converts the trained PPE detection model to ONNX format.

final_inference.py
➤ Performs two-stage inference: detects persons first, then detects PPE on them.
